high_descs: Turn back and walk towards the cabinet.
Open the cabin door which is under the sink and take the fork out of it and close the door.
After taking the fork, just move closer to the sink.
Put the fork in the sink, clean the fork off, and pick the fork back up.
Turn right and walk straight and again take a right turn and take a walk to enter into the right side room. Then walk towards the coffeetable.
Place the fork next to the bread slices on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Place the Fork on the CoffeeTable

high_descs: Turn around and go near the cabinet table.
Take the fork from the cupboard of the table.
Put the fork into the sink.
Washed the fork and take it out from the sink.
Turn around and go near the coffeetable.
Put the fork on the coffeetable near the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Placed the fork on the CoffeeTable from the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the cabinet
Pick up fork from the cabinet
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the sink on your right
Place fork inside the sink and then take it out
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the coffeetable
anns.task_desc: Washing fork on the sink and placing it on coffeetable
